bullet_descriptions: Fabric Weight Type: Year Round Fabric Construction
Product Name: Just Love Summer Dresses for Women - Placement Print Smocked Sundresses
Care and Cleaning: Machine Wash, Tumble Dry

bullets: KEEPS YOU COOL: These pretty sundresses for women are made using high quality 95% polyester and 5% spandex to create a light, flowing dress that keeps you comfortably cool even in the hottest of weather.
EASY FIT: We stock a variety of sizes all the way from S-3X, with our unique casual summer dresses having a smocking design at the chest to accommodate everyone from petite to plus size.
SIMPLE YET ELEGANT: Gorgeous patterns complement the nice elegant design, allowing you to wear the floral summer dress to the beach, to a lunch date, or simply when out and about.
WASHES WELL: These cute and sexy summer dresses do not lose shape or run color when properly cleaned, and are machine-safe for a quick and hassle-free wash.
GREAT VALUE: Just Love is all about giving you new fun summer dresses of the highest quality at the most affordable price around.
